<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <link rel="stylesheet" type="text/css" href="/css/styles.css">
    <title>Home</title>
</head>
<body>
    <header>
        <h1>Booklist</h1>
    
    </header>
    

    <div class="Function">
        <div class="title">Displaying all books:</div>
        <div class="code">/books</div>
        <div class="desc">Should return JSON list of all of the books in the database.</div>
    </div>

    <div class="Function">
        <div class="title">Finding Book by ID:</div>
        <div class="code">/api/books/:bookID</div>
        <div class="desc">By putting this in with an existing book ID, you will get a JSON object will all of the book information. </div>
    </div>

    <div class="Function">
        <div class="title">Creating New Books:</div>
        <div class="code">/api/books/add/:title/:authorName/:published_year/:token</div>
        <div class="desc">You will fill in the title, author name, publishing year, and the admin token and a new book will be added to the database.</div>
    </div>

    <div class="Function">
        <div class="title">Deleting Books:</div>
        <div class="code">/api/books/delete/:title/:token</div>
        <div class="desc">By entering the title and admin token the book will be deleted from the database.</div>
    </div>

    <div class="Function">
        <div class="title">Finding books:</div>
        <div class="code">/api/v1/book/query</div>
        <div class="desc">By putting in a name or word found in a book title all books will appear. </div>
    </div>

    <div class="Function">
        <div class="title">Finding Authors books:</div>
        <div class="code">/api/v2/author/query</div>
        <div class="desc">By entering an authors name all books entered under that author will be returned.</div>
    </div>

    <div class="Function">
        <div class="title">Update / Edit:</div>
        <div class="code">/api/books/edit/:title/:authorName/:published_year/:token</div>
        <div class="desc">Put in the book title and adjust anything from the book. In the order title, author name,published year, and admin token.</div>
    </div>

</body>
</html>